videos.description: UNC wins the jump ball as the crowd gets fired up.
videos.headline: The crowd is hyped in Chapel Hill for Senior Night

videos.description: Justin Jackson gets open on the break for a big time dunk after Duke turns it over.
videos.headline: Duke turnover leads to Jackson dunk

videos.description: Frank Jackson knocks down a 3-pointer from the wing after Jayson Tatum finds him with a sweet dish.
videos.headline: Tatum kicks it out to Jackson for three

videos.description: A great hustle play from Grayson Allen to beat Theo Pinson for the loose ball and then find Jayson Tatum for the dunk.
videos.headline: Allen dives for the loose ball, finds Tatum for the dunk

videos.description: Isaiah Hicks botches an easy dunk attempt and Duke capitalizes on the other end.
videos.headline: Hicks' missed dunk leads to three for Tatum

videos.description: Grayson Allen draws the foul on Justin Jackson and buries a 3-pointer, much to the dismay of the crowd in Chapel Hill.
videos.headline: Allen knocks down 3-pointer and-1 over Jackson

videos.description: Grayson Allen draws a foul but appears to throw an elbow and receives a technical foul for it. Allen hears it from the crowd on his way to the free throw line as Chapel Hill boos.
videos.headline: Grayson Allen back in the middle of controversy with elbow

videos.description: Amile Jefferson beats Isaiah Hicks for a layup with some nice footwork.
videos.headline: Jefferson puts the moves on Hicks

videos.description: Jayson Tatum blows by the UNC defense and throws down a big dunk.
videos.headline: Tatum throws down a rim-rattling dunk

videos.description: Grayson Allen gets open on the break off the UNC miss and buries a 3-pointer from the corner.
videos.headline: Allen buries a three from the wing

videos.description: Joel Berry II blows by the Duke defense and gets the floater to go. Can UNC hang on in Chapel Hill?
videos.headline: Berry II gets the floater to go

videos.description: Jay Bilas breaks down North Carolina's 90-83 win over Duke when Joel Berry II's offense provided a boost and how North Carolina's second-half defense wore down Duke.

tracking.trackingName: COM_NCB Analysis (Berry's offensive aggression fuels Tar Heels' win) 2017/03/04 SC

videos.headline: Berry's offensive aggression fuels Tar Heels' win

videos.description: No. 5 UNC takes down No. 17 Duke with Joel Berry II scoring 28 points in a 90-83 victory.
videos.headline: Berry leads UNC past Duke
